Test suites for llm-foundry

Overview
--------

This folder contains unit and integration test scripts for the foundry code base.

Available test scripts:

* tests_ddp.py: CPU-only pre-flight suite for the DDP training stack (imports, configs, MFU, dataloaders, model setup, optimizers, utilities, integration, trainer).
* tests_fsdp.py: CPU-only pre-flight suite for the FSDP training stack (imports, configs, MFU, dataloaders, model setup, optimizers, utilities, integration, trainer).
* tests_gym.py: End-to-end verifier and sample-generation checks for the gym pipeline (instruction, long-context, haystack, math, email, and tool-call tasks).

Both scripts are designed to run as standalone Python files and resolve module imports from their respective source folders.

Running Tests
-------------

From the repository root:

* `python tests/tests_ddp.py`
* `python tests/tests_fsdp.py`
* `python tests/tests_gym.py`


Notes
-----

* All test scripts set `sys.pycache_prefix` to `tmp/pycache` in the Linux temp directory (via `tempfile.gettempdir()`).

